title: Kenzie Elizabeth On Navigating Your 20's & 30's, Finding Purpose & Passion, & Never Giving Up
itunes:title: Kenzie Elizabeth On Navigating Your 20's & 30's, Finding Purpose & Passion, & Never Giving Up
description:
#466: On today's episode we are joined by Kenzie Elizabeth. Kenzie is the host of the ILYSM podcast, a creator, and vlogger. Today Kenzie joins the show for a discussion around how to navigate your 20's and 30's and how to find your purpose and passion. We also discuss how not giving up is a superpower and what you can do to never give up.
